functional_units.name: Synthetic Edit List Fixtures Generation
functional_units.description: Generates synthetic edit list fixtures (empty, single-offset, multi-segment, rate-adjusted) via generate_fixtures.py and publishes them to the fixture catalog.

functional_units.name: Fixture Metadata Extension
functional_units.description: Extends fixture metadata to include VR-014 warning coverage information and new JSON export snapshots.

functional_units.name: Regression Tests for Edit List Fixtures
functional_units.description: Runs regression tests that assert VR-014 warning coverage for various edit list scenarios using snapshot comparisons.

functional_units.name: JSON Export Snapshot Testing
functional_units.description: Executes Swift test cases to validate JSON export snapshots for empty, single-offset, multi-segment and rate‑adjusted edit lists.

functional_units.name: Documentation Update for C14d Completion
functional_units.description: Updates project documentation to mark C14d as complete and direct follow-up work to C15 and Validation Rule #15.
